<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <title>Main Page</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/base.css">
    <style>
        /* 메뉴 스타일 */
        .navbar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: #05445E;
            height: 80px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .navbar button {
            background-color: #189AB4;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }

        .navbar button:hover {
            background-color: #75E6DA;
            transform: scale(1.1); /* 버튼 커짐 */
        }

        /* 화살표 강조 */
        .navbar button::after {
            content: "⬇"; /* 화살표 아이콘 */
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30px; /* 버튼 아래에 위치 */
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            font-size: 20px;
            color: white;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
        }

        .navbar button:hover::after {
            opacity: 1;
            transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(10px); /* 화살표 위로 이동 */
        }

        /* 콘텐츠 스타일 */
        .content {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #189AB4, #75E6DA); /* 그라데이션 배경 */
            height: calc(100vh - 80px);
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .content h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: white;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* 배경 요소 (원형 애니메이션) */
        .background-circles {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            animation: move 10s linear infinite;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        /* 애니메이션 */
        @keyframes move {
            0% {
                transform: translateY(100vh) translateX(0);
                opacity: 0.8;
            }
            50% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: translateY(-100vh) translateX(20px);
                opacity: 0.3;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <button onclick="navigateTo('summary')">텍스트 요약</button>
        <button onclick="navigateTo('doc')">문서</button>
        <button onclick="navigateTo('voice')">음성</button>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <h1>다목적 AI 요약 서비스에 오신 것을 환영합니다.</h1>
        <p>상단에 있는 원하는 요약 서비스를 선택해주세요.</p>
        <!-- 배경 애니메이션 -->
        <div class="background-circles">
            <div class="circle" style="width: 100px; height: 100px; left: 20%; animation-delay: 0s;"></div>
            <div class="circle" style="width: 150px; height: 150px; left: 40%; animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
            <div class="circle" style="width: 200px; height: 200px; left: 60%; animation-delay: 4s;"></div>
            <div class="circle" style="width: 80px; height: 80px; left: 80%; animation-delay: 1s;"></div>
            <div class="circle" style="width: 120px; height: 120px; left: 50%; animation-delay: 3s;"></div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function navigateTo(page) {
            if (page === 'summary') {
                window.location.href = '/summary-page';
            } else if (page === 'doc') {
                window.location.href = '/doc-upload';
            } else if (page === 'voice') {
                window.location.href = '/voice-upload';
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
